ities resulting from securities issued that do not fall under point (a) ⟨liabilities resulting from securities issued with an effective maturity of one year or greater ‖ and/or liabilities resulting from securities issued with an effective maturity of less than one year⟩ ‖ and/or any other liabilities❭❯ in order to allow an assessment of the availability of stable funding
